    "id": 47,
    "offset": 351172,
    "slot_size": 250,
    "data_size": 246,
    "nom_orig": "Yukino",
    "texte_orig": "Lisa[SP]looks[SP]so[SP]much[SP]calmer[SP]now.[SP]She's[SP]very\ndetermined[SP]now...[SP]Like[SP]a[SP]woman[SP]who's[SP]figured\nout[SP]just[SP]what[SP]she[SP]wants.",
