  {
    "id": 50,
    "offset": 351964,
    "slot_size": 280,
    "data_size": 276,
    "nom_orig": "Yukino",
    "texte_orig": "The[SP]Last[SP]Battalion[SP]was[SP]the[SP]Fuhrer's[SP]special\nunit[SP]from[SP]way[SP]back,[SP]right?[SP]Why[SP]would[SP]people\nthink[SP]they[SP]were[SP]the[SP]ones[SP]who[SP]did[SP]this?",
