    "nom_orig": "Yukino",
    "texte_orig": "I[SP]wonder[SP]how[SP]many[SP]of[SP]them[SP]there[SP]are.[1205][U+000F][SP]Seriously,\nthey[SP]keep[SP]showing[SP]up,[SP]one[SP]after[SP]another...",
